textAfterTable: Profile AXA Aedificandi is an open-end fund registered in France. The objective of the Fund is to achieve capital appreciation. The Fund invests mainly in stocks and other related equity securities. The Fund invests at least 55 percent of its assets in equities related to the real estate sector. The Fund may invest in bonds and other debt securities.
